UID:4DPm4hEeoGRgiZwU88bKg
SUMMARY:Twelfth Night Ensemble
DTSTAMP:20260413T004621Z
DTSTART:20260503T140000Z
DESCRIPTION:Influenced by the sounds of today\\\, and with a vision for the
	 future\\\, the New York–based Twelfth Night Ensemble was formed “with the
	 firm belief that art is best explored as a meeting place of the past\\\, 
	present\\\, and future.” Timeless works by Handel\\\, Vivaldi\\\, Marais\\
	\, J. S. Bach\\\, and Destouches offer an illuminating vantage point and t
	horoughly rewarding musical experience in this unique exploration of human
	ity’s relationship to nature. \\n\\nEvents are offered for informational\\
	\, entertainment\\\, and educational purposes only. Read Town Hall’s Progr
	am Content Policy.\n\nhttps://townhallseattle.org/event/twelfth-night-ense
	mble/\n\nFrom Town Hall Seattle
